@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual --------------------------------------------------- break() -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "Functions" "break()"
@{U}break()@{UU}

@{B}sypnosis:@{UB}
   @{B}break([@{I}x @{UI}])@{UB}

@{B}arguments:@{UB}
   @{I}x @{UI}: any expression

@{B}result:@{UB}
   n/a

   Terminates the evaluation of the current  block. If you specified @{I}x @{UI},  this
will be the result of the block.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ ę by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
@ENDNODE
@NODE "FKT-CEIL"
@TITLE "ceil()"
@NEXT "FKT-CLOCK"
@PREV "FKT-BREAK"
@TOC "Functions"
@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual ---------------------------------------------------- ceil() -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "Functions" "ceil()"
@{U}ceil()@{UU}

@{B}sypnosis:@{UB}
   @{B}ceil(@{I}x @{UI})@{UB}

@{B}arguments:@{UB}
   @{I}x @{UI}: number, tensor

@{B}result:@{UB}
   number, tensor

   Return the integer that is bigger than or equal to @{I}x @{UI}. For complex numbers
@{I}ceil () @{UI} is applied separately to the real and imaginary part of @{I}x @{UI}.

   @{I}ceil () @{UI} on a tensor is applied on each member of the tensor.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ ę by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
@ENDNODE
@NODE "FKT-CLOCK"
@TITLE "clock()"
@NEXT "FKT-COLS"
@PREV "FKT-CEIL"
@TOC "Functions"
@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual --------------------------------------------------- clock() -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "Functions" "clock()"
@{U}clock()@{UU}

@{B}sypnosis:@{UB}
   @{B}clock()@{UB}

@{B}arguments:@{UB}
   n/a

@{B}result:@{UB}
   number

   Returns the number of seconds since system startup. It returns a floatpoint
value (4.5 means four and a halve seconds). The precision depends on the oper-
ating system.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ ę by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
