@{B}result:@{UB}
   number

   Returns @{I}x! @{UI} (factorial). If @{I}x <= 0 @{UI}, @{I}0 @{UI} is returned. Currently this is lim-
ited to @{I}170! @{UI}, because Laplace works internally with 64 bit floatpoints.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ ę by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
