   Set the visible area of  the plotter referenced by @{I}handle  @{UI}. If only @{I}xmin @{UI}
and @{I}xmax @{UI} are supplied,  @{B}auto scale@{UB} is enabled  and the Y-range is calculated
automatically. If you supply @{I}ymin @{UI} and @{I}ymax @{UI}, @{B}auto scale@{UB} is disabled.


